    "media:imagetext": "TWA AMBASSADOR SERVICE\nWELCOME ABOARD\nCocktail and Meal Service will begin shortly after take off ...\nappetizer\nFRESH SALMON SLICES\nRemoulade sauce\n#: $\n# 3 # 4p\n# #\nentrees\nBEEF BROCHETTE\nCharbroiled tender chunks of choice filet mignon\nserved with braised celery heart and parisienne potatoes\nSWEET \u0026 SOUR PORK LOIN\nCubes of deep fried pork loin in a subtle sweet and\nsour sauce .....\n...accompanied by yeung chow fried rice\nCHICKEN TAI - PO\nDelicate pieces of spring chicken pan fried with rich piquante soya beans\nto complement this entree we present Cantonese fried noodles\nI # 36 N\nDinner Roll\nCreamery Butter\n* 1 * 1\nthe sweet course\nFrom our bake shop we present a rich and delicate pastry\nJasmine Tea\nTWA's Freshly Brewed Coffee\nMilk\nTea",
